    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一击必杀</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用能力短暂控制时间流速，在合适的时机弹反斩杀敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/4fb5e2a9b4c9c1a32c42bb533257f67d.poster.avif?t=1769655770\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/4fb5e2a9b4c9c1a32c42bb533257f67d.webm?t=1769655770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/4fb5e2a9b4c9c1a32c42bb533257f67d.mp4?t=1769655770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双生角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由切换时空身份，灵活使用不同角色技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/ad94e4f63adf9379382331310ee8725a.poster.avif?t=1769655770\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/ad94e4f63adf9379382331310ee8725a.webm?t=1769655770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/ad94e4f63adf9379382331310ee8725a.mp4?t=1769655770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>机制交互</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同时空的场景会存在不同的特殊机关，智取比爽杀更有意思。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/4c882034e70f5f232e58b3c03c6eac8e.poster.avif?t=1769655770\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/4c882034e70f5f232e58b3c03c6eac8e.webm?t=1769655770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/4c882034e70f5f232e58b3c03c6eac8e.mp4?t=1769655770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多重结局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你有可能遇到来自不同时空的NPC，你的行为抉择将会使他们成为朋友，或者敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197180/extras/76da8735cd4aa40db4dae12ea01f45af.avif?t=1769655770\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦踏上旅途，命运的轮回就会开始转动。</p>",
